rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg001
rows.name:
I made tea for everyone.
Help yourselves!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg002
rows.name:
Oh no. Homura getting it
completely wrong...

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg003
rows.name:
Oh, would you rather have
something else, Tora-kun?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg004
rows.name:
Oh, no no, that not it. Tora just
think that your every move
was far from being from first-class maid.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg005
rows.name: ...Maid?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg006
rows.name:
Tora! Homura kindly made tea for us, 
you know?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg007
rows.name:
Oh, Tora know that, but, also...
Strive for perfection is important goal!
Tora feel very strongly about this!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg008
rows.name:
Moe is an essential element 
in a maid's demeanor and conduct.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg009
rows.name: Homura still quite lacking in moe!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg010
rows.name: I-It can't be...!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg011
rows.name: But what is "moe"?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg012
rows.name: It, uh...what every man looking for.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg013
rows.name:
If you master the art of "moe," 
you can captivate the hearts 
of all men!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg014
rows.name: A-all men? Really?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg015
rows.name: Of course!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg016
rows.name:
Homura, don't take anything 
Tora says seriously.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg017
rows.name: But...

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg018
rows.name:
Are you interested in learning 
the true essence of being a maid, 
Homura?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg019
rows.name: A-am I interested?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg020
rows.name: Yes I am!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg021
rows.name: If you think Rex would like that...

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg101
rows.name: Hey, Homura!?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg102
rows.name:
Good attitude! Tora will teach
maid art of moe.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg103
rows.name:
Come on, 
my greatest maid!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg104
rows.name: Welcome back Masterpon-kyun!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg105
rows.name: H-Hana-chan?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg106
rows.name:
What the hell happened to you?
Is this some kinda malfunction?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg107
rows.name:
Hana's Maid Mode has been
activated. Kyun!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg108
rows.name:
Greatest Maid Hana will teach you all
about essence of maid behavior.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg109
rows.name:
Moe is external magnification
of love feelings inside heart.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg110
rows.name:
Hana will teach magic way to magnify
love feelings. Chant with Hana.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg111
rows.name: U-Understood!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg112
rows.name: Please taste good, moe-kyun!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg113
rows.name:
Homura? You're not... 
going to... are you?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg114
rows.name: P-please t-taste-good? Moe...kyun!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg115
rows.name: And there we go...

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg116
rows.name:
Not quite!
Copy Hana exactly!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg117
rows.name: Yes, coach!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg118
rows.name:
Please, Homura... Come back to us...
While you still can!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg201
rows.name:
Boss is boy, so he definitely
not immune to the charms of
moe.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg220
rows.name:
It definitely worth Homura's time
to learn essence of maidiness.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg221
rows.name: I see...

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg202
rows.name:
Okay, I'm ready!
Tora-kun, tell me what to do!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg203
rows.name: Uh, Homura?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg204
rows.name:
Now I'll have you master 
the true essence of "moe"! 
Come here, ultimate maid!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg205
rows.name: Welcome home Onii-chan Kyun-kyun!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg206
rows.name: H-Hana-chan?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg207
rows.name:
What is this, Tora,
some kinda malfunction?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg208
rows.name:
Don't worry, Hana is currently 
in full 'moe moe mode' for Rex!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg209
rows.name:
Onii-chan, do your best salvaging! 
Kyun-kyuuun!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg210
rows.name: O-Onii-chan?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg211
rows.name: S-so this is "moe"...?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg212
rows.name: Okay, Homura, copy what Hana say.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg213
rows.name:
Onii-chan,
Hana is totally moe-kyun just for you.

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg214
rows.name:
O-Onii-chan...
Homura is totally...moe-kyun...
just for you!?

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg215
rows.name:
No good! That weak level of moe 
won't be enough to win 
over Boss' heart!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg216
rows.name: Try again!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg217
rows.name:
Onii-chan!
Homura is totally moe-kyun!
Just for you!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg218
rows.name: Not there yet!

rows.label: kizunatalk017_msg219
rows.name:
I...I give up.
I can't watch this any more.
